OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FIn the film we see them during a ten
OL,7,Fday stay at a therapy centre in
OL,8,FEstonia. They gradually share their
OL,9,Fexperiences of being told they'd be
OL,10,Fgiven new parents and in Veronika's
OL,11,Fcase days spent in solitary
OL,12,Fconfinement.
OL,14,FIt was when Vladimir Putin was charged
OL,15,Fwith the illegal deportation of
OL,16,FUkrainian Children by the
OL,17,FInternational Criminal Court that
OL,18,FBritish Filmmaker Sarah McCarthy
OL,19,Fdecided she had to tell their story.
OL,20,FMcCarthy's mother is Ukrainian, so
OL,21,Fthis project was personal for her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
