OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,F"The thought of being separated from
OL,7,Fmy own child is unimaginable," said
OL,8,FMcCarthy.
OL,10,F"And so as soon as I read that the
OL,11,FInternational Criminal Court had
OL,12,Fissued an arrest warrant for Vladimir
OL,13,FPutin for the illegal deportation of
OL,14,FUkrainian children, I knew that I
OL,15,Fwanted to find a way to tell that
OL,16,Fstory."
