OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FThis week, Sarah came to Beijing where
OL,7,Fshe is being hosted by the British,
OL,8,FUkrainian and Estonian embassies.
OL,9,FThere are plans to take the film to
OL,10,FAfrica and South America, and McCarthy
OL,11,Fhopes to introduce the story of
OL,12,FUkraine's stolen children to a wider
OL,13,Faudience where Russia's propaganda has
OL,14,Ftaken hold.
OL,16,F"We're here in China and my Chinese
OL,17,Ffriends and colleagues tell me the
OL,18,Fparty line has been that Ukraine
OL,19,Fstarted the war and Russia was
OL,20,Fdefending itself, which is patently
OL,21,Funtrue," explains McCarthy.
