OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FShe added: "It's scary to live in a
OL,7,Fworld where the President of the
OL,8,FUnited States is starting to parrot
OL,9,FRussian propaganda talking points."
OL,11,FOn Russian State Television, children
OL,12,Ftaken forcibly from Ukraine, have been
OL,13,Fparaded like they were rescued, rather
OL,14,Fthan kidnapped.
OL,16,FThere are still more than 19,000
OL,17,Fchildren being kept illegally in
OL,18,FRussia.
