OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FSasha and her siblings were taken at a
OL,7,Fmilitary checkpoint in the Donetsk
OL,8,Fregion when she was just five years
OL,9,Fold.
OL,11,FTheir father Yvgeny was held at a
OL,12,Fcorrectional facility and tortured for
OL,13,F45 days. When he was released, he
OL,14,Ffound his house had been bombed, he
OL,15,Fhad no food or money, but his priority
OL,16,Fwas to try to get his children back.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
