OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FWith the help of volunteers and
OL,7,Fseveral charities working to bring
OL,8,FUkrainian children home, Yvgeny was
OL,9,Fable to track his children down to an
OL,10,Forphanage in Moscow and by some
OL,11,Fmiracle they were given permission to
OL,12,Fleave.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FThe other girl featured in the film,
OL,20,FVeronika, is 14 years old.
