OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FShe was taken when the village she was
OL,7,Fin was captured by Russian soldiers.
OL,8,FShe was first taken to a camp in
OL,9,FRussia, then to a state orphanage
OL,10,Fwhere she was placed in isolation for
OL,11,Fseven days.
OL,13,FHer physical and mental health both
OL,14,Fsuffered, and her weight dropped
OL,15,Fdramatically.
OL,17,FVeronika's mother serves in the
OL,18,FUkrainian military and managed to
OL,19,Fraise her daughters' case at the UN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
