OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FBut it was her grandmother Vera who,
OL,7,Fafter one failed attempt to enter
OL,8,FRussia, managed to find Veronika and
OL,9,Fbring her back with the support of the
OL,10,FRed Cross and other NGOs.
OL,12,FIn the film Vera describes herself as
OL,13,Fa simple, rural woman, who nobody
OL,14,Fbelieved could achieve what she did.
OL,16,FThree months after his invasion of
OL,17,FUkraine, in May 2022, Putin signed a
OL,18,Flaw that fast-tracked Russian
OL,19,Fcitizenship for children from Ukraine
OL,20,Ffacilitating their fostering and,
OL,21,Fultimately, adoption.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
