OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FSome of the illegally deported
OL,7,Fchildren were taken from state
OL,8,Forphanages.
OL,10,FOthers were separated or displaced
OL,11,Fduring the fighting.
OL,13,FPutin has tasked his Children's Rights
OL,14,FCommissioner Maria Belova with
OL,15,Foverseeing the process.
OL,17,FShe has appeared on State television
OL,18,Ftransporting children on state
OL,19,Fairplanes, introducing them to their
OL,20,F'new parents' and has adopted at least
OL,21,Fone Ukrainian child herself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
