OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FThe children who have been rescued,
OL,7,Fincluding Sasha and Veronika, have
OL,8,Fshared their testimonies with the
OL,9,FInternational Criminal Court to help
OL,10,Fbuild the war crimes case against
OL,11,FPutin.
OL,13,FSarah intentionally did not include
OL,14,Fany war images in the documentary,
OL,15,Ffeeling that audiences have become
OL,16,Fimmune to bombs and burning buildings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
