OL,3,C'After the Rain': The stolen children
OL,4,Cof Russia's war in Ukraine
OL,6,FShe chose to let the stories of Sasha
OL,7,Fand Veronica tell a different side to
OL,8,Fthe war and, in their own words,
OL,9,Fexpose the innocence that is being
OL,10,Fstolen from Ukraine's children.
OL,12,F"I think the power of this film is
OL,13,Fthat it gives a platform to the
OL,14,Fchildren, you know, and the children,
OL,15,Fthey tell you very matter-of-factly
OL,16,Fwhat happened to them," McCarthy
OL,17,Fobserves.
